Package ch.usz.c3pro.c3_pro_android_framework.questionnaire.logic

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ConditionalStep
    This Interface defines the methods used for ConditionalSteps which can be added to ConditionalOrderedTasks and are only shown to the user when certain conditions are met.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConditionalInstructionStep
    This Class extends the ResearchStack InstructionStep and implements the C3PRO ConditionalStep.
    ConditionalOrderedTask
    This class extends the ResearchStack OrderedTask and can display Steps as well as ConditionalSteps.
    ConditionalQuestionStep
    This Class extends the ResearchStack QuestionStep and implements the C3PRO ConditionalStep.
    Items2Steps
    This class provides the tools to create ResearchStack Steps from FHIR Questionnaire.QuestionnaireItemComponents.
    Questionnaire2Task
    This is a static class that will provide the conversion of a FHIR Questionnaire Resource to a ResearchStack Task that can be used with a ResearchStack ViewTaskActivity to conduct a survey.
    ResultRequirement
    This class implements the logic of Questionnaire.QuestionnaireItemEnableWhenComponents.
    TaskResult2QuestionnaireResponse
    This class provides the tools to create a FHIR QuestionnaireResponse from a ResearchStack TaskResult
